display_long_description:
Green Garden – A VR Botanical Experience 🌿
Step into Green Garden, a fully immersive virtual reality experience where you can explore and interact with a beautifully designed botanical environment. Discover exotic plants, engage with nature, and enjoy a relaxing yet educational journey in a unique VR setting.

Key Features:
✅ Explore a detailed greenhouse environment – Designed to showcase a carefully curated selection of plants.
✅ Interactive mechanics – Scan, water, and fertilize plants while observing their real-time reactions.
✅ Dynamic environment – Experience realistic lighting and environmental effects that adapt to different times of the day.
✅ Immersive sound design – Enjoy high-quality ambient sounds that enhance the atmosphere and realism of the experience.
✅ Relaxing and educational – Learn fascinating details about plant species while immersing yourself in a peaceful, interactive world.
